| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0155 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1b78177a-dce3-5c08-b437-7aebd94e97ed"
